
CI - trigger build, 
  test build(success/ fail)
  trigger tests (success/fail)

continuous delivery - 
 CI success  -->  Automatically deliver to UAT  -->  Push a button manually to trigger deployment  -->  Automatically deploy to prod as official release  

continuous deployment -
  CI success  -->  Automatically deliver to UAT                  -->                                    Automatically deploy to prodas official release


UAT - 
It is a type of testing performed by end user or client to verify/accept the final build for production release. It is done after functional, intergration and system tetsing is done.

Capybara and Rspec - for acceptance testing. It test the application from the perspective of a human client. The test code walks through a userâ€™s browser interactions.

